{"tid":1601071,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益］ 航拍新屋嶺","createTime":"2019-09-29T01:24:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T02:04:13.000Z","uid":67321,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b3b3e19345ecad4a263e383890dbd6194e7281ce","tid":1601071,"uid":67321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T01:24:54.000Z","msg":"琴日見到另一個post 有新屋嶺既相<br />\n其實大家有冇諗過可以航拍新屋嶺<br />\n數番入同出既人數<br />\n當然要影到樣<br />\n因為對家好古惑 會喬裝成唔同人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當人地轉場唔用新屋嶺 航拍都跟住轉場<br />\n<br />\n同埋示威現場都可以用航拍<br />\n航拍者可以係室內 <br />\n會冇咁危險<br />\n<br />\n呢度咁多旅行jj 一定有航拍機<br />\n大家覺得有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c892d51654bf1a1aefe486be7f2ecd7244d73ad6","tid":1601071,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T01:30:56.000Z","msg":"航拍邊有咁多電維持咁耐"},{"pid":"65023c675a88a458f11d65f95a3a6745be7c46bc","tid":1601071,"uid":67321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c892d51654bf1a1aefe486be7f2ecd7244d73ad6","tid":1601071,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T01:30:56.000Z","msg":"航拍邊有咁多電維持咁耐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T01:31:33.000Z","msg":"所以唔可以得一部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f972310c1d612dbd8a860c2047fc7c329db19d5c","tid":1601071,"uid":286546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T01:33:38.000Z","msg":"用幾部拍 每部集中拍唔同位置 10分鐘電量一定夠"},{"pid":"693bf8b1e5ea1f8865417b6aa3cdd3cb8bdc9091","tid":1601071,"uid":67321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T02:06:35.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"b1e6908b2c97b67bbca7b22411bb36b4bf7ca165","tid":1601071,"uid":67321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T02:06:49.000Z","msg":"推2/10"},{"pid":"82aeabdb812540dc05551934b25ecca9e16323a6","tid":1601071,"uid":67321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim